# Play Pong Bot

## Install
To install this package, run the following

    python3.8 -m venv .
    . bin/activate
    python -m pip install -r requirements.txt

## Configuration
First, we must get our twitter api keys
    #file: API_ENV
    export PLAY_PONG_BOT_CONSUMER_KEY="MY_TWITTER_CONSUMER_KEY"
    export PLAY_PONG_BOT_CONSUMER_SECRET="MY_TWITTER_CONSUMER_SECRET"
    export PLAY_PONG_BOT_TOKEN_KEY="MY_TWITTER_TOKEN_KEY"
    export PLAY_PONG_BOT_TOKEN_SECRET="MY_TWITTER_TOKEN_SECRET"
